  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 17-23-1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO  REMOVE THE REQUIREMENT THAT A COUNTY HAS RECEIVED FUNDING FOR NO MORE THAN EIGHT ROUNDS FROM THE RURAL FIRE TRUCK ACQUISITION ASSISTANCE PROGRAM IN ORDER TO RECEIVE ADDITIONAL MATCHING ASSISTANCE UNDER THE PROGRAM; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
